@host = http://localhost:5078

### Create a blog (audited as alice, raises BlogCreatedEvent)
POST {{host}}/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User: alice@demo.dev

{
  "title": "Interceptors in EF Core"
}

### Create another (falls back to the demo user)
POST {{host}}/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Soft Delete Done Right"
}

### List blogs (soft-deleted rows hidden)
GET {{host}}/api/blogs

### Soft delete a blog (replace the id; audited as carol)
DELETE {{host}}/api/blogs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-User: carol@demo.dev

### List including deleted (IsDeleted=true rows still present)
GET {{host}}/api/blogs/with-deleted

### Outbox messages written by the OutboxInterceptor
GET {{host}}/api/outbox
